Bertram+Kimball+Little+Obituary&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.americanantiquarian.org%2Fproceedings%2F44517818.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABertram+K.+and+Nina+Fletcher+Little\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Nina-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Nina_10-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Gerard Wertkin, Editor. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=0fxMzYkMwqoC&amp;pg=PA2&amp;lpg=PA2&amp;dq=Abby+Aldrich+Rockefeller+Folk+Art+Collection+colonial+williamsburg+john&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=A8w6fPrIpu&amp;sig=mhCKMBsMAt5GHNBwmoPFLlBWZO4&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0ahUKEwizh4Tf2JrUAhXCWSYKHfJzBfc4FBDoAQgjMAA#v=onepage&amp;q=Abby%20Aldrich%20Rockefeller%20Folk%20Art%20Collection%20colonial%20williamsburg%20john&amp;f=false\">\"Encyclopedia of American Folk Art, page 2\"</a>. Routledge, 2004.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Encyclopedia+of+American+Folk+Art%2C+page+2&amp;rft.pub=Routledge%2C+2004&amp;rft.au=Gerard+Wertkin%2C+Editor&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3D0fxMzYkMwqoC%26pg%3DPA2%26lpg%3DPA2%26dq%3DAbby%2BAldrich%2BRockefeller%2BFolk%2BArt%2BCollection%2Bcolonial%2Bwilliamsburg%2Bjohn%26source%3Dbl%26ots%3DA8w6fPrIpu%26sig%3DmhCKMBsMAt5GHNBwmoPFLlBWZO4%26hl%3Den%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D0ahUKEwizh4Tf2JrUAhXCWSYKHfJzBfc4FBDoAQgjMAA%23v%3Donepage%26q%3DAbby%2520Aldrich%2520Rockefeller%2520Folk%2520Art%2520Collection%2520colonial%2520williamsburg%2520john%26f%3Dfalse&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABertram+K.+and+Nina+Fletcher+Little\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span><span class=\"citation-comment\" style=\"display:none; color:#33aa33; margin-left:0.3em\">CS1 maint: Extra text: authors list (<a href=\"/wiki/Categ